Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:52.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く どきやがれ！ この…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ うう…｡\Nもしも～し！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.10,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hello there! Huh, now what was that?!
