Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:22.46,Main,Racist Dickhead,0,0,0,,I didn't know this joint served filthy pigs like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:22.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(男性)この店は あんな臭え\N豚野郎を入れてんのか？
Comment: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.40,Main,Racist Dickhead,0,0,0,,Huh?! {Maybe leave this one out?} {Yeah, commented it out.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ～!?
